      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2009-01-21</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-02-23T21:25:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Homeland Security Transparency Act of 2009 - Amends the Homeland Security Act of 2002 to direct the Secretary of Homeland Security to: (1) require homeland security grant recipients to submit quarterly reports describing the nature and amount of each expenditure made using grant funds; and (2) publish such information and make it publicly available on the Department of Homeland Security's (DHS's) website.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
