      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Homeland Security Act of 2002 to direct the Secretary of Homeland Security to require, as a condition of receiving a homeland security grant, that a grant recipient submit reports on each expenditure made using grant funds.</title>
